-Share the MV on SNS platforms
-Watch 2-3 other videos in between before coming back and watch the MV again
-Don't use a playlist (unless you have to sleep or work)
-DON'T use "incognito mode"
-If you stream on several devices, use different accounts for each device
-DON'T refresh the page or pause the video
-DON'T mute the video in the app/website. use a headphone or mute it physically(vollume of the headphones for example if it has a Vol Wheel).
_________

-DON'T Loop the song
-Use the title track focused playlist, switch to other playlists with the song
-Go to big curanted playlists (e.g Today Top Hits) and play the song occasionally
-Interact with the platform regularly
-Share the song on SNS platforms
-Offline streams are counted, just make sure to reconnect later so the system can count your streams
-Stream with free account on spotify, IF you stream with paid accounts on other platforms
---------------------
ğŸš¨Itunes/apple musicğŸš¨
-Buy the Tracks in the album SEPARATELY, DO NOT "complete the Album" 
-Delete the song from the library after a purchase before streamin on Apple msic, otherwise your stream will not count.
-If you remove your download correctly, there should be a "plus +" sign next to the song when you stream
-For those who purchasing it on different Itunes accounts, you need to link each to separate devices (i.e. one device for each account)
-For Non-IOS users, you can download itunes on your PC and buy the single
